name: 10 inches Whisperdolls (Spring)
description:
Spring is a 10 inches sweet little girl, made of cotton interlock fabric, stuffed with sheep wool, with natural yarn for the hair, and embroidered face.

She comes with a sweet outfit and the fabric used for clothing is cotton.

I really like the details of my dolls. It takes considerable time and effort (the details make the difference). I hope you like her, she is very cute and one of the kind.

SHIPPING WITHIN US: $12.00
SHIPPING OUTSIDE US: ASK ME BEFORE YOU BUY HER.
